Dialogue: 5,0:02:01.18,0:02:04.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Vai buscar mais comida!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:04.45,0:02:06.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We've got money! - OG}A gente tem dinheiro agora!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:06.30,0:02:08.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The alcohol today sure tastes good! - OG}A bebida de hoje tá ótima!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:12.61,0:02:16.21,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{I've drawn graffiti on the walls\Nof people's houses for all these years. - OG}{I've decorated houses with graffiti for years.}Ninguém supera os anos que\Neu passei grafitando paredes.{Flashback to Gaimon @03:10}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:25.79,0:02:28.46,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{That huge amount of money... they stole it. - OG}Nosso dinheiro... eles levaram tudo.{Flashback to Water Seven 03 Timestamp 30:06}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:28.46,0:02:29.17,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Nami...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:30.50,0:02:35.63,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{I can't face everyone. - OG}A tripulação... não consigo encarar eles.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:37.12,0:02:40.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Make sure you beat up\Nevery one of them, guys! - OG}Acabem com todos eles, galera!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:47.11,0:02:48.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So that's what you wanna do? - OG}Então é isso?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:48.35,0:02:50.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{See? You lose. - OG}Viu? Perdeu!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:50.40,0:02:52.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Now, go buy some food! - OG}Agora, vai buscar a comida!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:52.40,0:02:56.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Make sure you buy all the food\Nat the store, okay?! We've got money! - OG}Compra tudo que tiver na loja,\Ntá?! A gente tem dinheiro!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:02.60,0:03:06.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Dammit. Just you wait and see.\NI'll beat you later. - OG}Droga! Espera só, que\Nna próxima eu ganho!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:12.88,0:03:14.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:27.22,0:03:29.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What?! What happened?! - OG}O quê?! O que foi isso?!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:34.00,0:03:35.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Someone's there! - OG}Quem tá aí?!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:35.41,0:03:37.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Who the hell are you jerks?! - GO}Quem diabos são vocês?!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:44.78,0:03:46.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esse é...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:55.54,0:03:58.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esse é...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:58.34,0:04:00.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha Luffy!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:12.71,0:04:16.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So you came to get the money back,\Nhuh, you fools? - OG}Então vocês vieram buscar o dinheiro\Nde volta, é? Que idiotice!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:16.15,0:04:21.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{See all the guys here?\NWhat do you think the four of you can do? - OG}Tá vendo todo mundo aqui? O que\Nvocês quatro acham que podem fazer?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:24.11,0:04:28.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But, well... you're here.\NYou've got a bounty on your head. - OG}Mas, já que tá aqui... dizem que\Nvocê tem uma recompensa pela cabeça.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:28.05,0:04:30.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So why don't you leave\Nthat head of yours with us? - OG}Então por que não deixa essa cabeça com a gente?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:31.70,0:04:34.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He's that weak long-nose's captain! - OG}Ele é o capitão daquele fracote narigudo!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:36.10,0:04:39.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He can't be that strong. - OG}Não pode ser {\i1}tão{\i0} forte assim!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:43.67,0:04:45.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Come on, shorty. - OG}Vem, baixinho!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:47.64,0:04:50.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:51.35,0:04:52.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hm? - OG}Hã?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:55.10,0:04:56.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que você tá fazendo?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:57.96,0:05:03.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He's punching? At that huge steel armor\Nthat even a battleship cannon can't shatter? - OG}Tá usando os punhos? Nem um canhão de\Nnavio de guerra amassa essa armadura de aço!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:03.50,0:05:04.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que piada!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:06.70,0:05:10.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If you're just fooling around,\NI'll go ahead and crush you! - OG}Se você tá só brincando,\Nvou te esmagar logo!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:27.80,0:05:29.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}...Cannon!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:36.44,0:05:40.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– O quê?!\N– O quê?!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:42.60,0:05:46.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{H-He punched a hole in that huge armor! - OG}E-Ele furou aquela armadura grossa!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:46.95,0:05:48.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:49.10,0:05:53.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{W-Wait a sec, you guys!\NLet's have a talk first! - OG}E-Espera aí, gente!\NVamos conversar primeiro!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:53.66,0:05:55.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Let's have a... - OG}Vamos conversar...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:55.23,0:05:57.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos... Vamos...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:57.12,0:05:58.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Let's fire cannonballs! - OG}Vamos atirar os canhões!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:58.82,0:06:00.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:03.00,0:06:04.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Three-Sword Style:
Dialogue: 5,0:06:05.35,0:06:06.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{Raven... - OG}Dire Raven...{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:12.80,0:06:13.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Hunt!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:27.19,0:06:30.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E-Essas balas de canhão\Nsão de ferro, sabia?!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:38.01,0:06:39.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Even a cannon, too! - OG}{\i1}E{\i0} o canhão?!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:39.67,0:06:43.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Encrenca! Esses caras são encrenca de verdade!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:44.13,0:06:48.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{G-Get out of here!\NGet out through the back door! - OG}V-Vamos cair fora! Saiam pela porta dos fundos!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:55.41,0:07:00.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You started the fight. Don't act pathetic. - OG}Vocês que começaram essa briga.\NNem pensem em fugir.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:00.90,0:07:02.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Party Table...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:03.23,0:07:05.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Kick Course!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:17.79,0:07:20.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{W-We can't use the back door! - OG}A-A porta dos fundos não dá!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:20.09,0:07:22.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The windows! Get out through the windows! - OG}As janelas! Tentem as janelas!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:23.25,0:07:24.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Rumble!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:25.30,0:07:26.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Horn Point!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:36.97,0:07:39.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Roseo Colonnade!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:45.87,0:07:48.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E-E-Espera aí, gente!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:48.61,0:07:51.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The money, right?!\NYou want the money back, right?! - OG}É o dinheiro, certo?! É isso que vocês querem!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:51.71,0:07:55.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Os 200 milhões de berry que aquele fracote tinha, né?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:55.03,0:07:59.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Infelizmente, o dinheiro não tá mais aqui!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:59.00,0:08:03.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nosso chefe, Mano Franky,\Npegou o dinheiro e foi fazer compras.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:03.59,0:08:07.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Since he's buying something on the black market,\Nwe don't know where he went. - OG}Ele tá negociando no mercado negro,\Nentão pode estar em qualquer lugar!{Ohms}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:07.91,0:08:12.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{In short no matter how much\Nyou go on a rampage here, that 200 million belly won't come ba– - OG}Resumindo, mesmo que vocês destruam tudo aqui,\Nos 200 milhões de belly não vão vol–
Dialogue: 5,0:08:12.51,0:08:14.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Era uma vez eu!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:14.14,0:08:16.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ahh! Zambai!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:18.01,0:08:23.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's enough out of you.\NIt has nothing to do with money. - OG}Cala a boca.\NIsto nunca foi sobre dinheiro.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:23.60,0:08:26.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É. Já é tarde demais.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:31.45,0:08:34.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We'll beat you up so bad that\Nnot even your bones will remain. - OG}Quando a gente acabar, nem\Nos ossos de vocês vão sobrar.{Z - Needs to match what Luffy is told in Water Seven 3 @05:34}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:34.74,0:08:36.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nem os ossos?!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:36.35,0:08:38.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You idiot! Don't get frightened! - OG}Seu idiota! Não se deixa intimidar!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:38.50,0:08:40.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,"Nem os ossos vão sobrar."
Dialogue: 5,0:08:40.13,0:08:44.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{is what we, the Franky Family,\Ndemolition workers and bounty hunters, say! - OG}Essa é a {\i1}nossa{\i0} frase! Nós somos a Família Franky,\Nespecialistas em demolição e caçadores de recompensas!{Z/Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:08:44.67,0:08:48.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mostra pra eles a especialidade da Franky House!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:55.00,0:08:57.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}{Anything Shot Cannon! - OG}Anything Goes Cannon!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:05.70,0:09:07.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Here they come! Attack them! - OG}Lá vêm eles! Acabem com eles!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:07.99,0:09:11.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{D-Don't flinch! Keep firing until we run out of cannonballs! - OG}N-Não recuem! Continuem atirando até\Nacabar a munição!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:11.79,0:09:13.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,São só quatro!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:31.40,0:09:32.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:33.14,0:09:35.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que barulho é esse? Fogos de artifício?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:35.45,0:09:38.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's from the northeast!\NThey're coming from the Franky House! - OG}Vem do nordeste...\NÉ da Franky House!{Z - CPS}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:38.51,0:09:42.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Them again? What's the fuss about this time? - OG}De novo eles? Que confusão é dessa vez?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:42.34,0:09:45.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yea-ugh! Shh! He'll hear us! - OG}É, é– Shh! Ele vai ouvir!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:48.69,0:09:51.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh, boy, they're getting too carried away. - OG}Putz. Eles vão destruir o lugar.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:51.50,0:09:56.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They really don't show any restraint\Nwhen they party, do they? - OG}Eles realmente não se controlam\Nnuma festa, né?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:56.49,0:10:01.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's okay once in a while, right?\NIt's a wonderful day today. - OG}De vez em quando tá tranquilo, né?\NHoje é um dia especial!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:18.29,0:10:20.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Shall we go follow Franky? - OG}Devemos ir atrás do Franky?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:20.30,0:10:21.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Where? - OG}Pra onde?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:23.01,0:10:27.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Damn. Looks like they reall\Ndon't know where the money is. - OG}Que saco. Parece que eles realmente\Nnão sabem onde tá o dinheiro.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:28.33,0:10:33.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Even if we strangle this Franky guy,\Nif he already spent the money... - OG}Mesmo se a gente enforcar esse tal Franky,\Nele pode já ter gasto o dinheiro.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:33.61,0:10:37.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What do we do now? Even if we wait for him here, he won't be back for a while. - OG}E agora? A gente pode esperar,\Nmas ele pode demorar pra voltar.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:38.37,0:10:40.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Terminei os primeiros socorros!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:40.94,0:10:44.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'd like to put him on a stretcher,\Nso help me out here! - OG}Preciso colocar ele numa maca. Me ajuda aqui!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:44.74,0:10:46.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Staying here talking won't get us anywhere. - OG}Ficar aqui falando não vai resolver nada.{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:46.96,0:10:51.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Let's go back to the ship for now.\NWe left Nami-san all alone there, too, so... - OG}Vamos voltar pro navio por enquanto.\NA Nami tá sozinha lá.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:51.20,0:10:53.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We have the thing\Nwith Robin-chan to deal with... - OG}Tem também a situação da Robin...{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:53.29,0:10:55.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,e os problemas com o navio também.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:55.89,0:10:56.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:57.21,0:10:58.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, Luffy!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:02.30,0:11:04.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sobre o navio...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:04.01,0:11:05.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:05.31,0:11:06.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I've made a decision. - OG}Eu decidi.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:16.42,0:11:20.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Let's say farewell to the Going Merry here. - OG}É aqui que a gente se despede\Ndo {\i1}Going Merry{\i0}.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:26.52,0:11:29.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well, then, I'm leaving now. - OG}Bom, vou indo então.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:31.70,0:11:34.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Seriously, what a stubborn guy he is. - OG}Sério, que cara teimoso.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:35.23,0:11:41.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Even though we don't know whether he has it or not, they send me out this far each time. - OG}A gente nem sabe se ele tem ou não,\Nmas me mandam até aqui toda vez.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:41.06,0:11:43.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Queria que se colocassem no meu lugar.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:49.20,0:11:50.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É a Kalifa.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:50.40,0:11:52.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom... pode entrar.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:53.91,0:11:56.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You must be worn out, Iceburg-[/i1]san[/i0]. - OG}Deve estar exausto, Sr. Iceburg.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:56.50,0:11:58.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Would you like something to drink? - OG}Quer beber algo?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:58.19,0:12:00.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:01.39,0:12:03.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll have some tea today. - OG}Hoje eu queria um chá–
Dialogue: 5,0:12:03.39,0:12:04.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I've prepared it. - OG}Já preparei.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:06.12,0:12:08.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well, just as I'd expect from you, Kalifa. - OG}Bom, isso é bem a sua cara, Kalifa.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:08.80,0:12:10.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Muito obrigada.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:13.85,0:12:16.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Mr. Corgi is always angry\Nwhen he leaves, isn't he? - OG}O Sr. Corgi sempre sai\Nde mau humor, né?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:16.99,0:12:19.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What on earth does he come to talk about? - OG}O que será que ele vem pedir?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:19.50,0:12:20.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yeah. - OG}Ah, isso.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:20.84,0:12:25.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He wants something I have,\Nso he suggests all sorts of deals. - OG}Ele quer algo que eu tenho,\Ne vive tentando me convencer a entregar.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:27.40,0:12:29.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Deve ser algo muito valioso, hein?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:29.85,0:12:35.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well, I always tell him that I don't know\Nwhat he's talking about and refuse. - OG}Bom, sabe... eu sempre digo que não sei\Ndo que ele tá falando e mando ele embora.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:35.55,0:12:38.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They really are a pain in the ass. - OG}Ele é muito chato.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:39.98,0:12:41.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:42.95,0:12:45.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! O Usopp acordou!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:45.82,0:12:48.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Really?! Good! - OG}Sério?! Que bom!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:49.90,0:12:51.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Agora podemos relaxar um pouco.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:55.36,0:12:56.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, Usopp!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:02.60,0:13:05.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A Robin{-chan} ainda não voltou.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:05.59,0:13:09.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Seriously, don't worry us so much! - OG}Sério, não nos preocupa desse jeito!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:10.80,0:13:15.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{She's right. To think that you marched\Nin by yourself. That was so reckless. - OG}Ela tem razão. Ir lá sozinho\Nfoi muito imprudente.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:15.49,0:13:18.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You were lucky that you didn't die. - OG}Você teve sorte de estar vivo.{Z/Ohms}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:18.40,0:13:20.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Think a little before you act. - OG}Pensa antes de agir da próxima vez.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:20.89,0:13:23.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Olha quem fala!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:25.90,0:13:29.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Just because I'm so good-for-nothing. I'm sorry! - OG}Desculpa por ser tão inútil!{Ohms}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:29.74,0:13:30.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Really. - OG}Tô falando sério...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:30.96,0:13:32.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm ashamed! - OG}Que vergonha!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:32.66,0:13:34.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vocês!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:37.87,0:13:40.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That money was so important for us\Nand yet, I let it... I let it... - OG}Aquele dinheiro era tão importante,\Ne eu deixei ele... eu deixei...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:40.77,0:13:44.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey, hold on a sec! Calm down! I-I get it already, let me go! - OG}Ei, calma! Se acalma!\NE-Eu entendi, me solta!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:44.38,0:13:48.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But the huge amount of money we got,\Nafter all that we went through. - OG}Não, é sério, a gente passou por tanta coisa\Npra conseguir aquele dinheiro e eu...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:48.93,0:13:51.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Usopp, você ainda devia estar na cama.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:51.90,0:13:56.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey, listen to what Chopper is saying. - OG}Ei, escuta o que o Chopper tá dizendo.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:57.30,0:13:59.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Then, as I was afraid... - OG}Então é isso.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:59.66,0:14:02.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{the money won't come back? - OG}O dinheiro foi embora de vez, né?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:02.50,0:14:07.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Bom, só vamos saber com certeza\Nquando esse tal Franky voltar.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:07.55,0:14:10.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Entendo. Desculpa.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:10.24,0:14:14.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Well, even if don't get it back,\Nwe still have the 100 million belly. - OG}Mas mesmo que a gente não recupere,\Nainda temos 100 milhões de berry.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:14.20,0:14:15.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So that's okay. Don't worry about it. - OG}Então tá tudo bem. Não se preocupa.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:19.00,0:14:21.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's not okay about the money! - OG}{\i1}Não{\i0} tá tudo bem! É o nosso dinheiro!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:21.54,0:14:22.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nami...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:22.51,0:14:24.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah! Foi mal.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:24.80,0:14:27.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No, that's okay. - OG}Não, ela tem razão.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:27.30,0:14:31.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But Luffy, what about the ship?\NWhat about the Merry? - OG}Enfim, Luffy, e o navio?\NE a {\i1}Merry{\i0}?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:31.30,0:14:34.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Can we somehow have her repaired\Nwith that remaining 100 million? - OG}Os 100 milhões restantes\Ndão pra consertar ela?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:35.15,0:14:38.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We're lucky that we can have her\Nrepaired in such a first-class shipyard. - OG}A gente tem sorte de estar num\Nestaleiro de primeira pra isso.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:38.52,0:14:43.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{In order for her to be able to travel\Nin the seas ahead, I'd like her to be stronger. - OG}Vamos ter que reforçar ela pra aguentar\Nos mares que vêm pela frente.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:43.61,0:14:45.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Usopp, about the ship. - OG}Usopp, sobre isso...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:45.53,0:14:47.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I decided to get a new ship. - OG}Nós vamos trocar de navio.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:47.80,0:14:51.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry that I made the decision\Nwithout consulting you, - OG}Desculpa por ter decidido sem te consultar,
Dialogue: 5,0:14:51.45,0:14:53.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,mas eu já me decidi.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:53.60,0:14:59.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O {\i1}Going Merry{\i0} cuidou bem da gente,\Nmas nossa jornada com ele acaba aqui.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:07.65,0:15:08.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Enfim...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:09.28,0:15:12.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I took a look at the catalog that Iceboss gave us. - OG}Eu dei uma olhada no catálogo que o Icechefe nos deu.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:15:12.22,0:15:16.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{While checking the ships in it,\NI noticed there're quite a few kinds. - OG}Tem um monte de tipos diferentes\Nde navios pra ver aqui.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:16.99,0:15:20.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If we get a used one, 100 million will allow us to buy a bigger ship than Merry. - OG}Se pegarmos um usado, 100 milhões\Ngarantem um navio bem maior que a {\i1}Merry{\i0}.{Z/Gaijin/Ohms}
Dialogue: 5,0:15:20.69,0:15:21.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espera aí...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:22.65,0:15:24.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Wait, wait. - OG}Calma, calma.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:15:24.24,0:15:29.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're taking\Nthe joke too far. That's ridiculous. Right? - OG}Essa piada... Você tá levando isso\Nlonge demais. Não acha?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:29.80,0:15:33.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{See? Chopper took it seriously. - OG}Olha só! O Chopper tá levando a sério.{Ohms}
Dialogue: 5,0:15:33.89,0:15:37.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Seriously, what'll we do with our captain? - OG}Sério, alguém manda o nosso\Ncapitão parar com isso.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:37.59,0:15:40.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Fala alguma coisa pra ele, Nami.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:43.70,0:15:48.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So, does that mean that we don't\Nhave enough money for the repair? - OG}Então quer dizer... que a gente realmente\Nnão tem dinheiro suficiente pra consertar?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:48.42,0:15:53.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Because I got that 200 million stolen by them, w-we're now short on money, right? - OG}É porque eu deixei roubarem\Nos 200 milhões, não é?!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:53.00,0:15:55.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, é isso que tá acontecendo, né, Luffy?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:55.23,0:15:58.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The cost of a first-class shipyard\Nwould also be first-class, so... - OG}Um estaleiro de classe mundial {\i1}cobraria{\i0}\Npreços de primeira, afinal...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:58.50,0:16:00.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não! Não é isso!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:00.18,0:16:04.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Then why is it?! Spit it out!\NAre you trying to be considerate to me?! - OG}Então o que {\i1}é{\i0}?! Fala logo!\NVocê tá pegando leve por minha causa?!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:04.73,0:16:08.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm not! It has nothing to do\Nwith that money being stolen! - OG}Não tô! Isso não tem nada a ver\Ncom o dinheiro que roubaram!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:08.82,0:16:11.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Then why are you saying stupid stuff like\Nthat we're gonna get a new ship?! - OG}Então por que essa ideia maluca\Nde trocar de navio?!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:11.82,0:16:13.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey, stop it, both of you! - OG}Ei, parem com isso, vocês dois!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:13.24,0:16:16.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What good will fighting do?\NCalm down and then talk! - OG}Brigar não vai adiantar!\NSe acalmem, {\i1}depois{\i0} conversem!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:18.41,0:16:21.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How can I calm down when\Nhe starts saying stupid stuff?!}Como eu vou me acalmar\Ndepois de ouvir essa besteira?!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:21.79,0:16:25.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey! This is an important matter.\NDon't get so worked up. - OG}Ei! Eu sei que é importante,\Nmas não se exalta assim.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:25.23,0:16:29.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{She's right, Usopp. You need to rest, or you won't get better. - OG}Ela tem razão, Usopp. Você vai piorar\Nse não ficar quieto.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:29.20,0:16:30.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Who cares about my body?! - OG}Quer saber, que piore!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:30.99,0:16:34.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How can I be quiet when our captain\Ncasually says we'll get a new ship?! - OG}Não dá pra ficar tranquilo quando o capitão\Nfala de boa que vai trocar de navio!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:34.61,0:16:38.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's not casual! I made the decision\Nafter agonizing over it! - OG}Não foi de boa! Eu decidi\Ndepois de pensar muito!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:38.20,0:16:40.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What and how did you agonize\Nover to make this kind of decision?! - OG}E o que exatamente te fez sofrer\Npra chegar nessa decisão?!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:41.28,0:16:44.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How dare you talk about it\Nwhile waving this stupid thing?! - OG}Você tem a cara de pau de falar isso\Nenquanto balança essa coisa?!{Z/Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:45.15,0:16:46.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What'd you do that for?! - OG}Por que fez isso?!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:46.85,0:16:48.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's an eyesore. - OG}Tava me irritando.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:48.50,0:16:52.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey, Luffy, if it wasn't because\Nwe got our money stolen, then why?! - OG}Me diz, Luffy, se não é por causa\Ndo dinheiro roubado, então por {\i1}quê{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:52.50,0:16:56.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Luffy, why don't you say it?\NWhy are you keeping quiet?! - OG}Hã, Luffy?! Fala logo!\NEi! Por que não me conta?!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:56.49,0:16:58.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If you're not being considerate to me,\Nthen don't hold back! - OG}Não segura nada, por mais que doa!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:58.72,0:17:02.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Say it! I won't accept it\Nunless I hear good reason! Hey! - OG}Fala! Por que eu deveria\Naceitar isso?! Hein?!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:02.79,0:17:04.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A {\i1}Merry{\i0} não pode...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:16.80,0:17:20.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What did you just say? - OG}O que... O que você acabou de dizer?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:20.86,0:17:23.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não me faz repetir.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:23.45,0:17:26.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A {\i1}Merry{\i0}... não tem conserto.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:26.80,0:17:29.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No matter what we do, she won't be fixed. - OG}Não tem... como consertar ela.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:31.78,0:17:35.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Otherwise, I wouldn't say something like that. - OG}Se tivesse, eu não estaria falando isso.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:35.15,0:17:39.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This ship?! Are you talking about this ship\Nthat we're on board right now?! - OG}{\i1}Este{\i0} navio?! Você tá falando do navio\Nem que a gente tá agora?!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:39.99,0:17:43.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's right. This ship will sink soon. - OG}Isso mesmo. Este navio não vai durar muito.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:46.46,0:17:48.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What're you talking about, Luffy? - OG}O que você tá dizendo, Luffy?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:48.80,0:17:52.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É a verdade. Eles disseram no estaleiro.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:53.89,0:17:57.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They said that she won't even reach the next island. - OG}Disseram que ela nem vai chegar\Nna próxima ilha.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:57.00,0:18:00.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É mesmo? Ela {\i1}não vai{\i0}, é?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:00.28,0:18:04.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So you were persuaded by strangers\Nyou just met today and gave up just like that? - OG}Você conheceu esses caras hoje, e eles já\Nte convenceram a desistir assim?{Ohms}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:04.41,0:18:06.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What'd you say? - OG}Como é?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:06.00,0:18:09.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Just because first-class shipwrights\Ntold you that this is it... - OG}Eu sei que esses carpinteiros de primeira\Nderam o diagnóstico, mas...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:10.90,0:18:13.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,você desistiu assim tão fácil?!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:13.89,0:18:16.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A gente viajou junto esse tempo todo!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:16.54,0:18:18.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We made it through all sorts\Nof waves and battles together! - OG}Por cada onda! Em cada batalha!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:18.64,0:18:21.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{She's our dear friend! - OG}Ela é uma companheira preciosa da tripulação!{Z}{Carried us through hell and high water! - Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:21.68,0:18:25.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Are you gonna abandon her\Nin a place like this?! - OG}E você vai simplesmente abandonar\Nela num lugar desses?!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:28.90,0:18:34.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Is that how little this\Nship means to you, Luffy?! - OG}É isso... É tão pouco que\Neste navio significa pra você, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:36.59,0:18:39.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Você não devia gritar desse jeito, Usopp.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:39.76,0:18:40.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por favor, saia da frente.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:40.85,0:18:41.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:43.60,0:18:46.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm not done talking to him. - OG}Eu ainda não acabei com ele.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:46.02,0:18:47.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Usopp...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:49.95,0:18:52.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Then can you make an accurate assessment?! - OG}{Okay, so you know better than them?! - OG}Então você consegue fazer\Num diagnóstico melhor?!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:53.62,0:18:58.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We don't have a shipwright on this ship. That's why we asked them to check her out! - OG}{\q2}A gente não tem carpinteiro.\NPor isso pedimos pra eles avaliarem!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:58.50,0:19:02.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Fine! We don't have to\Nask those guys to fix her! - OG}Tá bom, mas pedir pra caras como eles\Nconsertarem é inútil!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:02.70,0:19:05.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll repair her, as I always have! - OG}Eu conserto ela como sempre fiz!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:05.88,0:19:08.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's how we've continued\Nto travel in the first place. - OG}Afinal, foi assim que a gente chegou até aqui.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:08.79,0:19:12.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Okay, let's start now. Hey, help me, guys! - OG}Beleza! Vamos começar agora!\NMe ajudem, galera!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:12.50,0:19:14.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, espera, Usopp.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:14.10,0:19:19.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah é, a gente não tem madeira suficiente.\NVou comprar no estaleiro.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:19.13,0:19:21.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Now, we're getting busy. - OG}Agora temos muito a fazer.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:21.18,0:19:23.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're not a shipwright, are you, Usopp?! - OG}Você não é carpinteiro naval, Usopp!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:23.60,0:19:24.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Espera, Luffy!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:25.80,0:19:28.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É, você tem razão. E daí?!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:28.10,0:19:31.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But I don't trust irresponsible shipwrights who easily give up on a ship - OG}Eu não confio em carpinteiros irresponsáveis\Nque abusam da posição{Ohms}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:31.39,0:19:37.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{just because it belongs to someone else by taking advantage of their position as craftsmen!}e descartam as coisas porque é\N"só mais um navio" pra eles!{Ohms}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:37.25,0:19:38.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Usopp...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:38.66,0:19:43.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This must be a lesson that we should\Nprotect our own ship by ourselves. - OG}A lição aqui...? A gente precisa\Ncuidar do nosso navio por conta própria.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:43.29,0:19:48.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu nunca vou desistir deste navio!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:48.84,0:19:50.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Are you guys stupid or what?! - OG}Vocês ficaram loucos?!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:50.60,0:19:54.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You probably got fooled by the shipwrights'\Nconvincing argument, didn't you?! - OG}Vocês todos caíram no papo bonito\Ndesses carpinteiros, não é?!{Ohms/Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:54.80,0:19:58.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The Luffy I know would've believed\Nin the strength of the Merry first. - OG}O Luffy que eu conheço não teria\Ncaído numa conversa dessas.{Ohms}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:58.92,0:20:02.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{rather than buying those guys' sales talk! - OG}Ele teria sido o {\i1}primeiro{\i0}\Na acreditar na força da {\i1}Merry{\i0}!{Ohms}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:02.72,0:20:06.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Such a clear-cut answer that sounds like one made\Nby an old man who understands everything. - OG}Mas você não hesitou, agindo como se fosse\Num velho sábio que sabe de tudo.{Ohms}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:06.81,0:20:09.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How can you make a decision like that,\Nsuddenly acting all captain-like?! - OG}Que tipo de capitão toma\Ndecisões precipitadas assim?!{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:09.79,0:20:12.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu me enganei sobre você, Luffy!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:12.36,0:20:14.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Wait a sec, Usopp! Luffy, too, first– - OG}Espera, Usopp! O Luffy também pensava a mesma–
Dialogue: 5,0:20:14.80,0:20:17.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Stay out of this, Nami!\NThis [/i1]is[/i0] something I decided! - OG}Fica fora disso, Nami!\NIsso {\i1}é{\i0} algo que só eu decidi!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:18.35,0:20:19.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I won't change my opinion. - OG}E eu não vou mudar de ideia.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:19.40,0:20:22.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No matter what you say now, we're gonna get a new ship! - OG}Não importa o que você diga,\Nnós vamos trocar de navio!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:22.44,0:20:24.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vamos nos despedir da {\i1}Merry{\i0} aqui!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:24.32,0:20:26.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't be ridiculous! I won't allow that! - OG}Nem ferrando! Eu não aceito isso!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:26.78,0:20:31.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Listen, Luffy! It's not like everyone\Ncan live looking ahead like you do! - OG}Escuta, Luffy! Nem todo mundo consegue\Nseguir em frente como você!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:32.25,0:20:35.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu não consigo deixar nossa amiga ferida aqui\Ne seguir em frente pros mares!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:35.92,0:20:39.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't be ridiculous! Even if she's our friend,\Nhumans and ships are different! - OG}Para com isso! Amiga ou não,\Nhumanos e navios são diferentes!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:39.60,0:20:42.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They're the same!\NMerry has the strength to live left in her! - OG}São a mesma coisa!\NA {\i1}Merry{\i0} ainda tem forças pra continuar!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:42.99,0:20:47.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Considering how you are, aren't you excited thinking about the new ship - OG}Mas te conhecendo, você provavelmente tá\Nempolgado pensando no navio novo.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:45.64,0:20:49.43,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{You can't have a conversation if you're worked up like that! - OG}Vocês não vão resolver nada tão alterados assim!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:47.17,0:20:49.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{while pretending to be concerned about Merry?! - OG}Não finge que se importa com a {\i1}Merry{\i0}!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:49.43,0:20:50.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Já chega!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:50.93,0:20:52.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:52.06,0:20:54.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't think that you're\Nthe only one who feels pain over this! - OG}Você não é o único que tá sofrendo com isso!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:54.29,0:20:55.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Everyone here feels the same way! - OG}Todo mundo aqui sente o mesmo!{Z - CPS}
Dialogue: 5,0:20:55.94,0:20:58.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If that's true, there's no way\Nyou'd decide to get a new ship! - OG}Se isso fosse verdade, não tinha como\Nvocê decidir trocar de navio!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:58.48,0:21:03.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Fine! If you dislike what I decide\Nthat much, then get off this– - OG}Tá bom! Se você detesta tanto as minhas\Ndecisões, então sai do na–
Dialogue: 5,0:21:07.13,0:21:08.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:14.61,0:21:19.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You idiot. What were you about to say?!}Seu idiota.\NO que você ia dizer?!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:19.21,0:21:23.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Cool down! Be careful\Nabout what you say! Got that, Luffy?! - OG}Se acalma antes de falar algo que\Nvai se arrepender! Entendeu, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:30.89,0:21:33.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Desculpa. Eu só...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:33.99,0:21:38.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's okay, Luffy.\NThat's how you really feel, isn't it? - OG}Tudo bem, Luffy.\NPode ser como você realmente se sente.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:38.50,0:21:39.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que você disse?!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:42.38,0:21:47.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Go ahead and cut off useless crewmates\None after another and move on. - OG}Pode ir descartando os companheiros inúteis\Num por um e seguindo em frente.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:48.36,0:21:50.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Se você vai abandonar a {\i1}Merry{\i0}...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:51.40,0:21:53.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{why don't you do that to me, too?! - OG}por que não faz o mesmo comigo?!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:53.29,0:21:56.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey, Usopp. Don't say stupid stuff like that. - OG}Ei, Usopp. Para de falar besteira.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:56.71,0:21:58.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não, eu tô falando sério.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:58.90,0:22:01.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I've been thinking about this for a while. - OG}Já faz um tempo que eu penso nisso.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:02.74,0:22:08.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{To be honest, I've been thinking that I can't keep up with your monstrous strength. - OG}Pra ser sincero, eu andei pensando que não consigo\Nacompanhar a força monstruosa de vocês.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:09.13,0:22:12.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Like today. I can't even watch over money. - OG}Como hoje, eu não consegui nem vigiar o dinheiro.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:14.47,0:22:19.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll just keep causing you guys trouble. - OG}Eu só vou continuar sendo um peso pra vocês.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:23.39,0:22:26.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You don't need weak friends, right? - OG}Vocês não precisam de companheiros fracos, certo?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:26.40,0:22:31.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy, você é o homem que\Nvai ser o Rei dos Piratas.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:31.89,0:22:35.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But I don't have to go that high up. - OG}Mas eu não preciso ir tão longe.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:22:36.71,0:22:43.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Thinking back, when I was about to set sail,\Nyou guys asked me to join you. - OG}Pensando bem, eu ia zarpar por conta própria,\Nquando vocês me convidaram pra entrar.{Z/Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:22:44.14,0:22:46.63,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,O que você tá esperando? Sobe logo.{Flashback: Last episode of Syrup Village, also referenced in Post War 08 @39:10}
Dialogue: 5,0:22:47.02,0:22:49.34,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,Você é um de nós agora, não é?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:53.19,0:22:54.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's all that's tying us together. - OG}É só isso que nos une.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:57.30,0:23:01.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We don't have to travel together\Nwhen we have a difference of opinion! - OG}Se a gente não concorda em nada,\Npor que viajar juntos?!{Z - Looks like this idiom doesn't need hyphens.}
Dialogue: 5,0:23:03.08,0:23:06.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, onde você tá indo, Usopp?!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:06.78,0:23:08.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pra onde eu vou é problema meu.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:09.20,0:23:12.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não tem mais nada a ver\Ncom vocês.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:13.64,0:23:14.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eu estou...
Dialogue: 5,0:23:18.08,0:23:21.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,saindo da tripulação.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:41.50,0:23:44.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Por que... Por que vocês não dizem nada?
Dialogue: 5,0:23:47.15,0:23:48.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:49.86,0:23:52.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Wait! It shouldn't be like this! - OG}Espera! Isso tá tudo errado!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:52.78,0:23:54.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Volta!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:54.57,0:23:56.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei! Volta aqui!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:56.20,0:23:59.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Não vai, Usopp!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:02.84,0:24:06.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Volta!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:06.09,0:24:07.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy...!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:16.40,0:24:20.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Luffy! I can't go along with you anymore. - OG}Luffy! Eu não consigo mais te seguir.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:21.60,0:24:24.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Sorry to cause you trouble until the end. - OG}Desculpa por ter sido um peso até o fim.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:26.69,0:24:30.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's true that the ship belongs to you, the captain. - OG}Eu sei que o navio pertence\Na você, o capitão.
Dialogue: 5,0:24:32.50,0:24:34.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So fight me. - OG}Então lute comigo por ela...
Dialogue: 5,0:24:34.90,0:24:36.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Monkey D. Luffy!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:44.60,0:24:47.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Have a duel with me! - OG}Eu te desafio pra um duelo!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:53.88,0:24:57.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê? O quê? E-Ei... O que você tá dizendo?!
Dialogue: 5,0:24:59.50,0:25:04.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hoje à noite, às dez horas, eu volto aqui.
Dialogue: 5,0:25:04.77,0:25:07.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Then we'll fight a duel over the Merry! - OG}Aí a gente vai duelar pela {\i1}Merry{\i0}!
Dialogue: 5,0:25:07.90,0:25:10.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll defeat you and take the Merry. - OG}Eu vou te derrotar e {\i1}ficar{\i0} com ela!
Dialogue: 5,0:25:10.80,0:25:11.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E depois...
Dialogue: 5,0:25:12.38,0:25:15.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,não vai sobrar nada nos unindo.
